data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Monroe, GA! This stunning home boasts an ton of features. Situated on 5 sprawling acres, this ranch-style home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you pull up the driveway, you'll see the covered RV parking straight ahead, providing cover for your camper or other big toy . Plus, with a 3rd car garage located in the basement, there's plenty of room for all your vehicles and toys. Step inside and discover a spacious and inviting interior, highlighted by high ceilings in the family room. The cabinets in the kitchen are custom-built and solid wood. The bonus room is off the kitchen area and has built in bookshelves. A half bath off the hallway allows guests to not need to go into the bedroom spaces. Also, the split bedroom plan ensures privacy and comfort for all. But the features don't stop there. Venture downstairs to find a full finished basement that's been set up as an in-law suite, complete with its own kitchen, bathroom, and living area with gorgeous custom fireplace. Need a space to tinker or work on projects? Look no further than the workshop in the basement, providing the ideal environment for DIY enthusiasts and hobbyists alike. And for additional storage needs, there's a convenient storage building located in the backyard. Outside, you'll appreciate the level lot and the serene, private setting that surrounds you. Located in a peaceful and quiet area, yet still within easy reach of amenities and conveniences, this home truly offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss your chance to make it yours – schedule a showing today and experience all that this remarkable property has to offer.
